TopicTitle: Kerbal Space Program 1.0 Career: An uncut journey to Duna pt.1

Articles.Content:
An unmanned rover mission to Duna.This time I've decided to give you an uncut experience. This will be good for those who are new to the game, haven't bought the game yet or just want to see the game as is. Each episode will be around 20-25 min. (Give or take)
